    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/32694cc39ac668f8571e33e97f38888a.poster.avif?t=1680860951\" width=616 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/32694cc39ac668f8571e33e97f38888a.webm?t=1680860951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/32694cc39ac668f8571e33e97f38888a.mp4?t=1680860951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在这款自走棋游戏中，召集技能各异的萌兽，组建队伍击败敌人！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/8d293e00a02a1a14d5d01eba658f271f.webp?t=1680860951\" width=300 height=40 /></span><br><br>在每局游戏开始时，你将能从数个随机萌兽中，召集你所需要的萌兽。除了攻击力、防御值、生命值皆不相同以外，一些萌兽还有独特技能，充分思考搭配不同的萌兽，将会使你的战队发挥最大战力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/b9e2a19e670fc19f663fd2bc27cc70d0.poster.avif?t=1680860951\" width=446 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/b9e2a19e670fc19f663fd2bc27cc70d0.webm?t=1680860951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/b9e2a19e670fc19f663fd2bc27cc70d0.mp4?t=1680860951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/7fe7dbd4377421b08c97f7262b6a3aea.webp?t=1680860951\" width=300 height=40 /></span><br><br>每只萌兽都可以升级！升级的萌兽将具有更高的攻击力、防御力、生命值，又或者更强大的技能！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/00213484795a97e49260b4fd062c458f.poster.avif?t=1680860951\" width=446 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/00213484795a97e49260b4fd062c458f.webm?t=1680860951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/00213484795a97e49260b4fd062c458f.mp4?t=1680860951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/e97529d35af4f618ee109aadf72a9204.webp?t=1680860951\" width=300 height=40 /></span><br><br>每一轮的对手将会更加强大，你的萌兽战队准备好了吗？迎接挑战吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/58aaae26a9aff302daf0e65b7cceab2a.poster.avif?t=1680860951\" width=446 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/58aaae26a9aff302daf0e65b7cceab2a.webm?t=1680860951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200390/extras/58aaae26a9aff302daf0e65b7cceab2a.mp4?t=1680860951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
